column2: an A.M. Eatery////Delish! We got the Pancake flight
column4: and one of the Benadicts. All were very very good! The peanut butter cup pancake is super rich but good
column5: sweet pot is nice and sweet but also light?
column6: The pineapple was soooooooooo good! Only down side is they do not offer coconut milk in coffee which is tastier in coffee vs almond milk for dairy free options.
